{"tid":1930721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[安已不] 有幾多連登仔其實心裏面係認同呢個日本仔 -「殘障者應死」兇徒刀刺19人日本戰後最大殺人案被判極刑","createTime":"2020-03-17T17:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T09:00:49.000Z","uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ef070b2598e82d5ab4b412fc2d44fcebf772519d","tid":1930721,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:52:54.000Z","msg":"2020-03-16 18:43<br />\n日本戰後最大宗殺人案，相模原殘障者設施殺人案在3月15日判刑。被告植松聖因涉嫌殺害19名院友，裁決殺人罪名成立，判處死刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200316/316278859366535168.jpeg/4gaotKfZmMeb2w1L-cNX5VJo3VzNzlR3guT-eILk_ng?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200316%2F316278859366535168.jpeg%2F4gaotKfZmMeb2w1L-cNX5VJo3VzNzlR3guT-eILk_ng%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=a834d582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相模原殘障者設施殺人案初審，3月15日於橫濱法院審結，判處被告死刑。(Reuters)<br />\n<br />\n事發在2016年7月，相模原一間殘障人士的療養機構的前職員，以「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">智障者不應在世上生存</span></strong></span>」為由，持刀闖入院內行兇，造成19名院友死亡共26人受傷。事件是日本戰後有紀錄以來，最大宗的殺人案，震驚全國。<br />\n<br />\n案件在3月15日初審作結，橫濱地方法院裁決指出，行兇者清楚意識自己所為，案件情節極嚴重，除極刑外無酌情餘地，裁決殺人罪成立，判處死刑。<br />\n<br />\n被告在裁決後曾舉手要求發最後一言，但被主審法官拒絕，直接閉庭。<br />\n<br />\n被告在過去曾表示<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">殘障人士浪費社會保障，應當殺害</span></strong></span>，被捕時亦多次面露笑容，被視為是性格扭曲，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">抱持極端優生主義的殺人犯</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽講唔少連登仔好憎廢老弱智殘障 <br />\n仲有咁多元首、夜神月支持者<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9ddf4674516ab9a6efebed5380a95356ec0529","tid":1930721,"uid":36049,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:59:11.000Z","msg":"連登仔得把口姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫左幾個月麻包袋有邊次真做<br />\n呢條友低賤好多<br />\n殺弱者,cls <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7383c67714fcea893f7b34e16cba12e9add993d8","tid":1930721,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T18:01:31.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎仲唔夠大殺傷力咩"},{"pid":"4fa1ecadc532aa60717780286195fa807df20037","tid":1930721,"uid":157411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T18:07:34.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎做緊"},{"pid":"3cc6c20b91358ca5416598c9a8d7a8989a04941e","tid":1930721,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T18:08:47.000Z","msg":"窮撚賤種先係"},{"pid":"f00534c7eaddf561ac0a84aa41a7485d1ca86884","tid":1930721,"uid":40997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"岩 所以佢腦殘都該死"},{"pid":"690a954f2ad2760344fdf5a2fa8e026365064e2f","tid":1930721,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f00534c7eaddf561ac0a84aa41a7485d1ca86884","tid":1930721,"uid":40997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"岩 所以佢腦殘都該死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:00:49.000Z","msg":"卿家所言定是 <br />\n呢類仆街亦都同佢口中嘅殘廢一樣，一定要仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}